comments: Allen (MEM) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball during Teague's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) has his hand rested on Brooks' (MEM) side as he starts his upward shooting motion and quickly removes it without applying any force.
Ojeleye (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Allen's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
Anderson (MEM) hedges the pick and cleanly dislodges the ball away from Smart (BOS). Smart momentarily re-gains control of the ball and Anderson cleanly dislodges him of the ball a second time.
Anderson (MEM) has his left arm extended outward and marginal contact occurs with Smart's (BOS) front as Smart defends the driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) and Brooks (MEM) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Williams III (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Brooks' (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
Brooks (MEM) rests his forearm on Brown's (BOS) side and marginal contact occurs before he releases away during Brown's driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Smart's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Williams III (BOS) has his arm extended slightly forward when marginal contact occurs with Morant's (MEM) front during the driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) delivers contact with his left shoulder to Valanciunas' (MEM) side and dislodges him from position.
Williams III (MEM) initiates contact across Morant's (MEM) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Williams III (BOS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Allen (MEM) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Smart (BOS) and marginal contact occurs when Allen brushes Smart's left arm during his upward shooting motion.
Teague (BOS) and Morant (MEM) come together at the same spot inside the perimeter and marginal contact occurs with Morant's side before they separate.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Ojeleye (BOS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Smart (BOS) brings his hand to Brooks' (MEM) right side and marginal contact occurs as Brooks spins away during the drive.
Valanciunas (MEM) backs up and marignal contact occurs with Theis (BOS) as he dunks the ball.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Morant's (MEM) path following the hand-off and absorbs the contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Teague (BOS) during his upward shooting motion.
Smart (BOS) and Valanciunas (MEM) engage and disengage with one another as Valanciunas rolls into the lane.
Ojeleye (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the body contact made with Anderson (MEM) at the start of Anderson's dribble.
Anderson (MEM) brings his off-arm toward Ojeleye's (BOS) front and marginal contact occurs as Anderson naturally releases away.

Ojeleye (BOS) has his hand rested on Anderson's (MEM) front as Anderson starts his upward shooting motion and marginal contact occurs before Ojeleye quickly removes it. Ojeleye then makes incidental "high-five" contact with Anderson after the release.
Smart (BOS) and Valanciunas (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Allen (MEM) legally contests Teague's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) brings his arm down and makes contact to Anderson's (MEM) arm during his shooting motion.
Allen (MEM) has his arm around Theis' (BOS) upper half before quickly sliding it off.
Allen (MEM) stops his forward momentum as he and Smart (BOS) come together along the perimeter and marginal contact occurs when Smart starts his upward shooting motion.
Brown (BOS) lunges forward and creates body contact with Brooks (MEM) at the start of his dribble.
Teague (BOS) places two hands on Allen (MEM) attempting to commit a take foul.
Theis (BOS) cleanly deflects the pass intended for Valanciunas (MEM).
Ojeleye (BOS) makes incidental contact with Morant's (MEM) left arm after Morant secures the loose ball.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Theis (BOS) and Valanciunas (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Brooks (MEM) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Teague (BOS) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Brooks (MEM) and Brown (BOS) make incidental contact with one another as Brown receives the inbound pass.
Valanciunas (MEM) turns into Brown (BOS) and creates body contact that affects Brown's driving shot attempt.
Brown's (BOS) free throw attempt does not make contact with the rim.
